org.jscsi.target.scsi.sense.senseDataDescriptor.senseKeySpecific

Packages that use org.jscsi.target.scsi.sense.senseDataDescriptor.senseKeySpecific
org.jscsi.target.connection.stage.fullfeature This package contains all classes which represent stages of the Full Feature Phase. 
org.jscsi.target.scsi.cdb This package contains all classes representing Command Descriptor Blocks (CDBs), which are used by the SCSI initiator to convey commands and parameters to the SCSI target. 
org.jscsi.target.scsi.sense This package contains all classes which represent SCSI sense data - data which gives a detailed account of current or deferred SCSI errors. 
org.jscsi.target.scsi.sense.senseDataDescriptor This package contains all classes that represent sense data descriptors, elements of sense data used to provide more specific error information. 
org.jscsi.target.scsi.sense.senseDataDescriptor.senseKeySpecific This package contains all classes representing sense-key specific data, which is a part of sense-key specific sense data descriptors.
